<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.4.1">
<l>āṭiyāṭi yakamka rain ticai</l>
<l>pāṭippāṭik kaṇṇīrmal kiyeṅku</l>
<l>nāṭināṭi naraciṅkā veṉṟu</l>
<l>vāṭi vāṭumiv vāṇutalē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Dancing, dancing, [her] heart dissolving, music</l>
<l>singing, singing, tears welling up, everywhere</l>
<l>searching, searching, saying “Narasiṃha!”,</l>
<l>fading she fades [away], this [girl with] bright forehead.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
